reviews.review_text: beautiful eyes great eyes version. long and intricate.i love the longer versions from earlier shows
dead space Hey great show thanks tapers!!!! but what is with the dead space after every song???
Really, really good! New baby steps of songs that became favorites.
First live Eyes of the World.. ..if I'm not mistaken. Someone mentioned it was good, and they weren't lying.

Epic I would have killed to be at this show.  It has an energy all it's own, that blend of a band at their peak in their old stomping ground of Palo Alto just laying it out.  The Pavillion floor must have been bouncing something fierce.  Truly one of my favorites.  I must of worn my old cassette of this show out I played it so oftern
